Courtesy of #DStv403 KWAZAKHELE - A suspect has been arrested in connection with eight murder cases in Kwazakhele, Gqeberha. The murders happened on 29 January. UPDATE:Â 8 dead in Gqeberha shooting Two gunmen entered a house where a birthday party was happening and started shooting. Eleven people were shot, eight of whom died, including the owner of the house. Police recently received information about the whereabouts of six suspects. When they arrived at the house Friday only one suspect was found. He will appear in court on Monday. Police are on the hunt for the remaining suspects who managed to flee.